cdse-s3.title: Copernicus Data Space Ecosystem S3
cdse-s3.description: This endpoint provides access to EO data which is stored on the Object Storage. A Global Service Load Balancer (GSLB) directs the request to either CloudFerro Cloud or OpenTelekom Cloud (OTC) S3 endpoint based on the location of the DNS resolver.
